018package com.github.tommyettinger.kryo.jdkgdxds;
019
020import com.esotericsoftware.kryo.Kryo;
021import com.esotericsoftware.kryo.io.Input;
022import com.esotericsoftware.kryo.serializers.MapSerializer;
023import com.github.tommyettinger.ds.ObjectObjectOrderedMap;
024
025public class ObjectObjectOrderedMapSerializer extends MapSerializer<ObjectObjectOrderedMap<?, ?>> {
026    public ObjectObjectOrderedMapSerializer() {
027        super();
028        setKeysCanBeNull(false);
029    }
030
031    @Override
032    protected ObjectObjectOrderedMap<?, ?> create(Kryo kryo, Input input, Class<? extends ObjectObjectOrderedMap<?, ?>> type, int size) {
033        return new ObjectObjectOrderedMap<>(size);
034    }
035
036    @Override
037    protected ObjectObjectOrderedMap<?, ?> createCopy(Kryo kryo, ObjectObjectOrderedMap<?, ?> original) {
038        return new ObjectObjectOrderedMap<>(original.size(), original.getLoadFactor());
039    }
040}
